OL,3,CMeet the woman taking her homeless
OL,4,Cstory onto stage and screen
OL,6,FA Bristol woman is using her
OL,7,Fexperience of homelessness to improve
OL,8,Fpeople's understanding of the issue.
OL,10,FAmanda Wall said she and her two
OL,11,Fchildren were moved 11 times in six
OL,12,Fweeks by Bristol City Council before
OL,13,Ffinding the home she's now had for two
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FShe said: "It was gruelling,
OL,17,Fdemoralising, frustrating. There was
OL,18,Fno consistency for the kids.
OL,20,F"They didn't know from one minute the
OL,21,Fnext where they would be living."
