OL,3,CMeet the woman taking her homeless
OL,4,Cstory onto stage and screen
OL,6,FShe added: "It's the judgement that it
OL,7,Fwas down to drugs, alcohol, any
OL,8,Fassumption, other than I could have
OL,9,Fbeen living in dire straits with a
OL,10,Flandlord who didn't do anything but
OL,11,Fnobody really wanted to know."
OL,13,FAmanda said that it was only by
OL,14,Ftelling her story publicly that her
OL,15,Ffamily's situation slowly started to
OL,16,Fimprove.
