OL,3,CMeet the woman taking her homeless
OL,4,Cstory onto stage and screen
OL,6,FNow she's got some stability in her
OL,7,Flife, the former singer-songwriter is
OL,8,Forganising a music and theatre
OL,9,Fproduction to perform publicly early
OL,10,Fnext year.
OL,12,F"I'm looking forward to the shows. I'm
OL,13,Flooking forward to making making money
OL,14,Ffor homeless families and homeless
OL,15,Fpeople and showing them there is light
OL,16,Fat the end of the tunnel," she said.
