OL,6,FThe Bristol hub of the homeless and
OL,7,Fhousing charity Shelter say increases
OL,8,Fin the number of homeless on the
OL,9,Fcity's streets and of families living
OL,10,Fin temporary accommodation will only
OL,11,Freduce when more social housing is
OL,12,Fbuilt.
OL,14,FAlly Rush, from Shelter, told ITV
OL,15,FNews: "There are over 1,500 families
OL,16,Facross Bristol living in temporary
OL,17,Faccommodation, including 1,700
OL,18,Fchildren.
