OL,3,CMeet the woman taking her homeless
OL,4,Cstory onto stage and screen
OL,6,F"We need families moving into
OL,7,Faccommodation that is genuinely
OL,8,Faffordable and social housing is the
OL,9,Fonly way as it's pegged to local
OL,10,Fincome."
OL,12,FBristol City Council figures show
OL,13,Fthere are more than 22,000 people on
OL,14,Fthe waiting list for social housing,
OL,15,Fwith total homelessness at a four-year
OL,16,Fhigh of more than 6,200 people.
OL,18,FThe authority said government funding
OL,19,Ffor temporary accommodation has been
OL,20,Ffrozen since 2011, leaving it to find
OL,21,F#13million for the last financial year.
