OL,4,Cstory onto stage and screen
OL,6,FBarry Parsons, chair of the homes and
OL,7,Fhousing delivery committee said:
OL,8,F"Bristol remains in the grip of a
OL,9,Fhousing crisis that is affecting every
OL,10,Fcommunity across the city.
OL,12,F"Growing demand for housing coupled
OL,13,Fwith rising costs and shrinking
OL,14,Favailability of affordable homes is
OL,15,Fpushing a growing number of households
OL,16,Ftowards homelessness.
