OL,3,CMeet the woman taking her homeless
OL,4,Cstory onto stage and screen
OL,6,F"We do not want to see families moved
OL,7,Ffrom hotel to hotel, which is why we
OL,8,Fare working hard to find a more
OL,9,Fsustainable way of providing safe and
OL,10,Fsettled accommodation for those most
OL,11,Fin need.
OL,13,F"There is no single solution to the
OL,14,Ftemporary accommodation crisis we and
OL,15,Fother councils face but it is clear
OL,16,Fthat whilst the housing crisis
OL,17,Fcontinues to cast a shadow over the
OL,18,Fcity, we will continue to face ongoing
OL,19,Fchallenges in ensuring support is
OL,20,Fthere for those who need housing."
