OL,3,CMeet the woman taking her homeless
OL,4,Cstory onto stage and screen
OL,6,FAmanda's show "FEAR", which stands for
OL,7,F"Families-Emergency-Accommodation-
OL,8,FRestart" has attracted the support of
OL,9,Fsome of Bristol's best-known artists.
OL,11,F"I feel strongly about the subject of
OL,12,Fhomelessness and the situation Bristol
OL,13,Fis in right now. That really wanted me
OL,14,Fto be part of the project," said DJ
OL,15,FQueen Bee.
OL,17,FWith a masters degree now to her name,
OL,18,FAmanda is determined to keep proving
OL,19,Fpeople wrong.
